					<!--cached-Mon, 21 Jul 2014 03:29:42 +0000-->Osc Sec does not whitelist filter the POST variables. There are a number of banned strings in POST variables, but it is left unfiltered in that manner so you should be able to use &#036; and , in a post. It does however whitelist filter the GET requests.
					
